description: Lists all jobs under the specified job collection.

top.description: The number of jobs to request, in the of range of [1..100].

nextlink.description: Gets or sets the URL to get the next set of jobs.

value.description: Gets or sets all jobs under job collection.

skip.description: The (0-based) index of the job history list from which to begin requesting entries.

filter.description: The filter to apply on the job state.
